snippet.textDisplay: So today is March 15th, 2025 Location Canada. And Im listening to this song. In few months it will be 2 years when it got all ended. I remember last year when i went back to India on February 28th just to meet her and make things good between us. I texted her that can we meet. She was not in the city at that time that’s what she said. She never said no to me but you can feel she doesn’t want to see you also. I was there for At least a month. I visited all places everyday where I used to spend time with her. Visiting all places just to remember those days when she was with me. I only got 1 chance just to see her. And i saw her just for fraction of seconds. Before coming back i text her one last time that I came back here just to meet you and make things correct but you never met. And what was most heartbreaking, she just live few meters away from my house and she saw me twice but never came to me. Since then my brain plays with me in my dreams looking for answers and making imaginations that she is back. All ik that she is with me…dont take it wrong. She lives in my heart, brain, dreams and most important Memories!
